#
# indicatif occupies a UNIQUE NICHE — the **CANONICAL Rust PROGRESS-
# REPORTING library**, sister to dialoguer R518's prompts and console's
# terminal primitives, all from the console-rs org.  Where Rust prompt
# libraries (dialoguer, inquire, cliclack) compete, **indicatif has NO
